<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أخبرنَا عَليّ بن نصر، ثَنَا الْحُسَيْن بن مُحَمَّد،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت عَمْرو بن عَليّ،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> سُلَيْمَان<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ابْن يسير،<span class="c5"> يكنى بِأبي الصَّباح:</span> مُنكر الحَدِيث<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> شُعْبَة وَغَيره.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣٩٨٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّباح:</span> مُحَمَّد بن شمر<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>الرعيني، مصري.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي عَليّ الهمذاني.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عبد الرَّحْمَن بن شُرَيْح.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أخبرنَا بكير بن الْحسن الرَّازِيّ بِمصْر، ثَنَا بكر<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>ابْن سهل، ثَنَا عبد الله بن صَالح، حَدثنِي<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أَبُو شُرَيْح عبد الرَّحْمَن بن شُرَيْح، عَن أبي<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>الصَّباح مُحَمَّد بن شمر.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣٩٨٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّباح:</span> سعيد بن سعيد<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>التغلبي.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">عَن:</span> سعيد بن عُمَيْر، عَن عقبَة بن دِينَار.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> وَكِيع بن الْجراح، وَأَبُو أُسَامَة<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وكناه.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أخبرنَا مُحَمَّد بن يُونُس، ثَنَا الْحُسَيْن بن مُحَمَّد<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت إِسْحَاق بن رَاهَوَيْه يذكر عَن أبي<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أُسَامَة فِيمَا قَرَأَ عَلَيْهِ، عَن سعيد بن أبي سعيد<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>أبي الصَّباح.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>٣٩٨٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّباح:</span> مُوسَى بن أبي كثير<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سعيد بن الْمسيب، وَمُجاهد.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> الثَّوْريّ، ومسعر وكناه.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>٣٩٨٩ - <span class="c2">(ق ١٦٨ / أ)</span> أَبُو الصَّباح<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>عبد الغفور الوَاسِطِيّ.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي هَاشم: مَتْرُوك الحَدِيث.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>قَالَه ابْن معِين.<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>سَمِعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> سَمِعت<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>عباسا،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> سَمِعت يحيى بن معِين يَقُول<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>ذَلِك.<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>٣٩٩٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّباح:</span> عمر بن قيس الماصر<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مسعر.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>٣٩٩١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّباح:</span> سَعْدَان بن سَالم<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>الْأَيْلِي.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عَطاء.<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>سَمِعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>عباسا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت يحيى،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span><a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>سَعْدَان ابْن سَالم الْأَيْلِي أَبُو الصَّباح.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span>٣٩٩٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّباح:</span> مُحَمَّد بن اللَّيْث<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span>الهداوي.<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> يحيى بن صاعد وَغَيره.<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>٣٩٩٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّباح:</span> الْوراق، مُؤذن<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p47"></span>وَاسِط.<a href="#p47" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p48"></span><span class="c5">عَن:</span> أم كثير.<a href="#p48" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>